<section class="case-hero">
        <h1>Start your case review</h1>
        <p>Tell us about your case and we will help you understand the right next step before you commit to more support.</p>
    </section>

    <main class="case-shell">
        <div class="case-intro">
            <p><strong>Use this form if:</strong> you are a new patient, want guidance before choosing a package, or already paid and need to hand off your case details.</p>
            <p><strong>Tip:</strong> If you already paid, mention the package in your message so we can move faster.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="case-grid">
            <div class="case-panel">
                <h2>Case review form</h2>
                <form id="consultForm">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>Full Name <span>*</span></label>
                        <input type="text" id="firstname" name="firstname" required placeholder="John Smith">
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>Email <span>*</span></label>
                            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required placeholder="john@example.com">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>Phone / WhatsApp</label>
                            <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="+1 234 567 8900">
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>Country <span>*</span></label>
                        <select id="country" name="country" required>
                            <option value="">Select your country...</option>
                            <option value="United States">United States</option>
                            <option value="United Kingdom">United Kingdom</option>
                            <option value="Canada">Canada</option>
                            <option value="Australia">Australia</option>
                            <option value="Japan">Japan</option>
                            <option value="South Korea">South Korea</option>
                            <option value="Germany">Germany</option>
                            <option value="France">France</option>
                            <option value="Singapore">Singapore</option>
                            <option value="Malaysia">Malaysia</option>
                            <option value="Indonesia">Indonesia</option>
                            <option value="Philippines">Philippines</option>
                            <option value="Thailand">Thailand</option>
                            <option value="Vietnam">Vietnam</option>
                            <option value="Russia">Russia</option>
                            <option value="Middle East">Middle East</option>
                            <option value="Other">Other</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>Medical Condition / Treatment Needed <span>*</span></label>
                        <select id="treatment_category" name="treatment_category" required>
                            <option value="">Select treatment type...</option>
                            <option value="Cancer Treatment / Oncology">Cancer Treatment / Oncology</option>
                            <option value="Proton Therapy">Proton Therapy</option>
                            <option value="Cardiac Surgery / Cardiology">Cardiac Surgery / Cardiology</option>
                            <option value="Orthopedics / Joint Replacement">Orthopedics / Joint Replacement</option>
                            <option value="Neurology / Neurosurgery">Neurology / Neurosurgery</option>
                            <option value="IVF / Fertility Treatment">IVF / Fertility Treatment</option>
                            <option value="Plastic / Cosmetic Surgery">Plastic / Cosmetic Surgery</option>
                            <option value="Dental Treatment">Dental Treatment</option>
                            <option value="Eye Surgery / LASIK">Eye Surgery / LASIK</option>
                            <option value="Traditional Chinese Medicine">Traditional Chinese Medicine</option>
                            <option value="General Health Checkup">General Health Checkup</option>
                            <option value="Other">Other</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>Describe Your Medical Situation <span>*</span></label>
                        <textarea id="medical_details" name="medical_details" required placeholder="Describe your condition, what you need, your timeline, and whether you already paid for a package."></textarea>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>How did you hear about us?</label>
                        <select id="source" name="source">
                            <option value="">Select...</option>
                            <option value="Google Search">Google Search</option>
                            <option value="Social Media">Social Media</option>
                            <option value="Friend / Referral">Friend / Referral</option>
                            <option value="Medical Tourism Directory">Medical Tourism Directory</option>
                            <option value="Other">Other</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>What do you need help with? <span>*</span></label>
                        <div class="checkbox-group" style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:12px;margin-top:4px;">
                            <label style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-weight:400;cursor:pointer;font-size:0.93rem;color:var(--text);">
                                <input type="checkbox" name="help_type" value="Hospital search / shortlist"> Hospital search / shortlist
                            </label>
                            <label style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-weight:400;cursor:pointer;font-size:0.93rem;color:var(--text);">
                                <input type="checkbox" name="help_type" value="Appointment coordination"> Appointment coordination
                            </label>
                            <label style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-weight:400;cursor:pointer;font-size:0.93rem;color:var(--text);">
                                <input type="checkbox" name="help_type" value="Airport pickup"> Airport pickup
                            </label>
                            <label style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-weight:400;cursor:pointer;font-size:0.93rem;color:var(--text);">
                                <input type="checkbox" name="help_type" value="Travel / route planning"> Travel / route planning
                            </label>
                            <label style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-weight:400;cursor:pointer;font-size:0.93rem;color:var(--text);">
                                <input type="checkbox" name="help_type" value="Not sure yet"> Not sure yet
                            </label>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>Preferred Service Path <span>*</span></label>
                        <div class="radio-group">
                            <label class="radio-item">
                                <input type="radio" name="package" value="Not sure yet - recommend a package" required>
                                <span><strong>Recommend a package for me</strong> - best for new visitors who have not paid yet</span>
                            </label>
                            <label class="radio-item">
                                <input type="radio" name="package" value="Hospital Match &amp; Plan ($49)">
                                <span><strong>Hospital Match &amp; Plan ($49)</strong> — 2-3 hospital matches + transport guidance + cost comparison</span>
                            </label>
                            <label class="radio-item">
                                <input type="radio" name="package" value="Pre-Arrival Coordination ($399)">
                                <span><strong>Pre-Arrival Coordination ($399)</strong> — full coordination: matching, hospital contact, pre-arrival planning, treatment support, discharge follow-up</span>
                            </label>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <button type="submit" class="submit-btn" id="submitBtn">Submit Case Review</button>
                    <p class="privacy-note">Your information is used only to review your case and recommend or deliver the correct service path.</p>
                </form>

                <div class="success-message" id="successMessage">
                    <div class="success-icon">✅</div>
                    <h3>Case submitted</h3>
                    <p>We have received your details and will review your case shortly.</p>
                    <ul class="success-next">
                        <li>Check your email for a confirmation message.</li>
                        <li>We usually reply within 4 business hours.</li>
                        <li>For faster response, message us on WhatsApp or WeChat.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div style="background:#f0f6ff;border-radius:16px;padding:20px;margin:24px auto;max-width:480px;text-align:center;">
                        <p style="font-weight:700;color:#1e3c72;margin:0 0 8px;">💬 Want a faster response?</p>
                        <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#4b5565;margin:0 0 16px;">Message us directly — we typically reply within minutes during business hours.</p>
                        <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
                            <a href="https://wa.me/8615763107083" class="cta-button" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#25D366 0%,#128C7E 100%);font-size:0.9rem;padding:12px 20px;" target="_blank" rel="noopener">💬 WhatsApp</a>
                            <a href="https://weixin.qq.com" class="cta-button" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#07C160 0%,#06AD56 100%);font-size:0.9rem;padding:12px 20px;" target="_blank" rel="noopener">💬 WeChat</a>
                        </div>
                        <p style="font-size:0.75rem;color:#999;margin:12px 0 0;">WeChat ID available upon request — or we'll share it when we reply to your email.</p>
                    </div>
                    <p style="margin:20px 0 12px;font-weight:700;color:#1e3c72;">Already know which package you need?</p>
                    <div class="success-actions">
                        <a href="pricing.html" class="cta-button" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#b78a42 0%,#d4a84b 100%);">Choose Package &amp; Pay →</a>
                        <a href="index.html" class="cta-button" style="background:transparent;color:#1e3c72;border:2px solid #1e3c72;">Back to Home</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="case-panel">
                <h2>Two ways to get started</h2>
                <div style="background:#f0f6ff;border-radius:16px;padding:20px;margin-bottom:20px;">
                    <p style="margin:0 0 8px;font-weight:700;color:#1e3c72;">✅ Not sure yet — Let us review your case first</p>
                    <p style="margin:0;font-size:0.95rem;color:#4b5565;">We review your case details, recommend the right package, and guide you on next steps.</p>
                </div>
                <div style="background:#fff8ef;border:1px solid #e8d5a8;border-radius:16px;padding:20px;margin-bottom:20px;">
                    <p style="margin:0 0 8px;font-weight:700;color:#b78a42;">💰 Already know which package you need — Pay directly</p>
                    <p style="margin:0 0 12px;font-size:0.95rem;color:#4b5565;">Go straight to pricing, choose your package, and pay with PayPal. Return here after payment if needed.</p>
                    <a href="pricing.html" style="display:inline-block;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#b78a42 0%,#d4a84b 100%);color:white;padding:10px 24px;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;">Pay Now →</a>
                </div>
                <div style="background:#e8f5e9;border:1px solid #a5d6a7;border-radius:16px;padding:20px;margin-bottom:20px;">
                    <p style="margin:0 0 8px;font-weight:700;color:#2e7d32;">💬 Prefer to chat first?</p>
                    <p style="margin:0 0 12px;font-size:0.95rem;color:#4b5565;">Message us on WhatsApp or WeChat. We typically reply within minutes during business hours.</p>
                    <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
                        <a href="https://wa.me/8615763107083" style="display:inline-block;background:#25D366;color:white;padding:10px 20px;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;font-size:0.9rem;" target="_blank" rel="noopener">💬 WhatsApp</a>
                        <span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;background:#07C160;color:white;padding:10px 20px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:700;font-size:0.9rem;">💬 WeChat: <code style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);padding:2px 8px;border-radius:4px;">Available via WhatsApp request</code></span>
                    </div>
                    <p style="margin:12px 0 0;font-size:0.85rem;color:#666;">📱 +86 157-6310-7083 · Mon-Fri 9:00-18:00 GMT+8</p>
                </div>
                <div class="link-actions" style="margin-top:24px; display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:16px;">
                    <a href="contact.html" class="cta-button">Other Contact Options</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
